- INI_ESECTION: header without ']' or empty name → column of '['. Non-blank text after ']' → column of that text.
- INI_EKEY: line without '=' → column of first non-blank char. Empty key → column of '='.
- INI_EQUOTE: unterminated → column of opening quote; unknown escape → column of backslash.
